Description: System tray indicator for Cloudflare WARP VPN
 WARP Indicator is a lightweight system tray application that provides quick
 access to Cloudflare WARP VPN connection status and controls. Monitor your
 VPN connection and toggle it on/off directly from your system taskbar.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time VPN status monitoring
  - Quick connect/disconnect toggle
  - Clean system tray integration
  - Lightweight Python implementation
  - Settings and information panels
